Class GeoShapeStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.mobility.sdk.map.GeoShapeStyle

    public abstract class GeoShapeStyle
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    Encapsulates the styling a geo shape that can be added to the map. See GeoShape.
